{"id":187090,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/10/【新闻联播送幸福了】黑龙江农场农民一年轻松收/","date":"2011-10-08T10:31:10Z","modified":"2011-10-08T10:51:07Z","title":"【新闻联播送幸福了】黑龙江农场农民一年轻松收入二三十万","content":"<p><span style=\"color: #4a4a4a;font-family: 宋体;line-height: 28px;background-color: #ffffff\"> </span></p>\n<p style=\"padding: 0px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\">【新闻联播送幸福了】</p>\n<p style=\"padding: 0px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\">昨晚的新闻联播，记者采访<span style=\"color: red\">黑龙江</span>农民，问一年收入多少？</p>\n<p style=\"padding: 0px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\">农民老刘：一年2、30万没问题，很轻松！</p>\n<p style=\"padding: 0px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\">共产党白给我们钱，现在就好几万。。。</p>\n<p style=\"padding: 0px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\">播音员旁白说：像老刘这样的收入在<span style=\"color: red\">黑龙江</span>是一般水平。</p>\n<p style=\"padding: 0px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\"><img class=\"quimby_search_image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;padding-top: 10px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\" src=\"http://bbsimg.shangdu.com/UserFiles/Image/415/61403415/1318035490195.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p style=\"padding: 0px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/10/66db3190tw1dlwf7fwd67j.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-187096\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/10/66db3190tw1dlwf7fwd67j.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"1014\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/10/66db3190tw1dlwf7fwd67j.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/10/66db3190tw1dlwf7fwd67j-130x300.jpg 130w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"padding: 0px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\">\n<p style=\"padding: 0px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\">\n","author":980,"categories":[20534],"tags":[8625,8782,9273]}